HEADWORD: Fettered
<hw>Fet"tered</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>Seeming as if fettered, as the feet of certain animals which bend
backward, and appear unfit for walking.</def>⟦br⟧
